condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section 1, para 2 | Description: The Borrower shall ensure that, until the completion of theProject, the PIU at all times functions in a manner satisfactory to the Bank with staff, consultants, facilities and otherresources. | Frequency: Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section 1, para. 3 | Description: The Borrower, through the PIU, shall carry out the Project inaccordance with the requirements, criteria, organizational arrangements and operational procedures set forth in the OM. |Frequency: Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, para. 4 (a) (i) | Description: (a) The Borrower, through the PIU, shall: (i) by notlater than October 31, 2015 or such other date as agreed with the Bank, sign the contracts for remaining procurement of goods withcontract duration of 12 months or more | Due Date: 31-Oct-2015

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, para. 4 (a) (ii) | Description :(a) The Borrower, through the PIU, shall: (ii) by notlater than June 30, 2016 or such other date as agreed with the Bank, sign all other contracts for activities included in theprocurement plan agreed upon between the Borrower and the Bank | Due Date: 30-Jun-2016

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, para. 4 (b) | Description: (b) If the Borrower, through the PIU, shall have failed tosign any of the contracts referred to above by the respective due dates, the Bank may, at its sole discretion, determine that theamount of the Loan pertaining to the unsigned contracts will not be required under the Project, and, without further notice to theBorrower, cancel such amount from the Loan Account | Frequency: Continuous

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, section 1, para. 1 | Description: At all times during the implementation of the Project, theBorrower shall maintain the IACC with a composition, resources and terms of reference satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency: Yearly

Finance Agreement: Schedule 2, Section II, para 1. | Description: The Borrower shall monitor and evaluate the progress of theProject and prepare Project Reports in accordance with the provisions of Section 5.08 of the General Conditions. | Frequency:Semi-annual
